==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὕδωρ, ὕδατος / hudōr  hudatos / hoo'-dor, hoo'-dat-os, etc.

===Etymology===
*From the base of G5205; water (as if rainy) literally or figuratively:

===Noun===
'''ὕδωρ'''

# [[water]].

